{
  "texts": [
    "The model is tested using data from 'DementiaBank' and it predicted AD with an AUROC of ~ 0.84.",
    "This model can be used as an alternative low-cost diagnostic method for early detection of AD.",
    "Also, integrating this model into AD clinical trials can substantially curb the cost and duration of clinical trials which in turn speeds up the drug development process.",
    "Cancer diagnosis and prognosis have highly benefited from the advancements in AI (Tanoli et al. 2021).",
    "The key diagnostic methods for cancer are the clinical imaging techniques (Fass 2008) such as X-ray, Computed Tomography (CT), and Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI)."
  ]
}